{"tid":724400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺d 10後小朋友講廣東話既比例仲高過00後","createTime":"2018-07-01T01:38:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-01T09:58:43.000Z","uid":171273,"like":67,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d89242a8be56a38f64c71bbc1537a35a86a67c5c","tid":724400,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T01:38:46.000Z","msg":"可能係佢地出世無耐本土意識就開始抬頭<br />\n<br />\n加上大多數10後父母都係8 90後居多 知道要保護粵語<br />\n<br />\n真係出親街聽到大多數10後小學生/幼稚園學生都係講廣東話<br />\n<br />\n反而中學果d就成日周街講蝗語<br />\n<br />\n不過都唔怪得佢地 做左中共文化入侵既受害者<br />\n<br />\n見到咁既情況有時會覺得班00後過多10幾年 會變成社會夾係中間比人睇唔起果一層"},{"pid":"7cd03ce8b0ea82b923b22b7207d54eff4f62d905","tid":724400,"uid":171273,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T01:41:24.000Z","msg":"上次係圖書館見到個10後 應該小三都唔夠<br />\n<br />\n同佢唔知阿麻定阿婆去 一路睇金庸一路讀比佢阿婆聽"},{"pid":"0a967d7f9b461745d67744a9b8ad9ebe68c0e24a","tid":724400,"uid":8040,"like":5,"dislike":21,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T01:41:35.000Z","msg":"你驚第日唔識蝗語比人歧視仲好<br />\n而家殖民速度仲快過本地出生率<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 唔識蝗語"},{"pid":"bdcec33b651c67a3bb2822fc2e4f3be54e7c19a9","tid":724400,"uid":143241,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T01:50:17.000Z","msg":"所以香港獨立要靠10後,因為啲00後信唔過"},{"pid":"625356eddfddbe2ff804ca613529dc78c568a118","tid":724400,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T07:23:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbc254885bce7f3b11b6437119abdc0ca2e8f548","tid":724400,"uid":38548,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T07:24:32.000Z","msg":"呢個真<br />\n<br />\n好多10後家長都好堅持個仔要講廣東話（同英文）"},{"pid":"0e69790b0c4391702a985685c8b3cf2e25aec45c","tid":724400,"uid":24227,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T08:47:22.000Z","msg":"係上水大埔馬鞍山都聽到好多講蝗語嘅小學雞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64a09ed12b24589e6fbe3e5f0f77d95e5